<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
For that reason, and to investigate the possibility of a class action lawsuit against the makers of the game, Woolley has tried to telephone his Internet friends, but they also are addicted and invariably hang up on her. <br>
